data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Waikoloa Village! This beautiful resort-style residence is in immaculate condition and is conveniently located with close proximity to schools, restaurants, shopping centers and the Waikoloa golf course.  Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this spacious home is fully air-conditioned and designed for comfort and relaxation. As you enter, dramatic high ceilings hallmark a sense of spaciousness and many windows and doors bring the outside in. The kitchen boasts Alder wood cabinets and Gialo Veneziano granite countertops, creating a perfect blend of style and functionality. The inside has been freshly painted with new flooring throughout, presenting a pristine and welcoming ambiance.  The outdoor wrap around deck is the place to enjoy morning coffee and watch the world go by, or have a glass of wine and take in the endless sunsets into the ocean.  Enjoy breathtaking panoramic views from your new home, showcasing the beauty of the blue ocean, mountains and ever changing colorful Hawaiian sunsets.   Step outside into your own piece of paradise - the beautifully landscaped yard created by a Master Gardner  has extensive new rock walls ensures both privacy and aesthetic appeal. A thoughtful drip irrigation system takes care of the lush greenery, making it easy to maintain the tropical oasis around your home.  Whether you're entertaining guests or simply unwinding after a long day, this property provides the ideal setting. Embrace the Big Island lifestyle in this meticulously cared-for residence that combines modern amenities with the natural beauty of Hawaii. Don't miss the opportunity to make this move in ready property your new home!
